{"title":"The Best Panoramic Photos of 2024","link":"https://kottke.org/24/10/the-best-panoramic-photos-of-2024","date":1728583320000,"content":"\n        <p>The results of the 15th annual Epson International Pano Awards have been announced â€” <a href=\"https://thepanoawards.com/2024-winners-gallery/\">you can check out all the winners &amp; runners-up on the competition website</a>. Here are a few of my favorites:</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/pano-24-01.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/pano-24-01.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/pano-24-01.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"650\" alt=\"an overhead view of a boat navigating rows of crops\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/pano-24-02.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/pano-24-02.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/pano-24-02.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"656\" alt=\"a lightning strike illuminates a mountainous landscape\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/pano-24-03.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/pano-24-03.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/pano-24-03.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"650\" alt=\"a wave crashes on rocks\" /></p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/pano-24-04.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/pano-24-04.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image